Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with distributed consensus and optimization over networks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the application of distributed optimization to machine learning problems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with control of networked systems. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the paper deals with communication networks. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses the impact of packet-dropping on information transmission.
